    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"21104\">This is a reminder that Liferay DXP 7.1&nbsp;reached end of life on November 13, 2025.</p>\n\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"21231\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Extended Premium Support (EPS)</strong></p>\n\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"21263\">If you have an active EPS subscription, you will continue to receive extended premium support until your EPS subscription expires.</p>\n\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"21395\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Recommended Actions</strong></p>\n\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"21416\">In order to receive Premium Support, subscribers must upgrade to a version in Premium Support such as Liferay DXP 2025.Q2.</p>\n\n<ul data-indent-level=\"1\">\n\t<li>\n\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"21555\">For information about the latest features and benefits of our current releases, please see <a data-renderer-mark=\"true\" href=\"https://www.liferay.com/web/guest/whats-new\" title=\"https://www.liferay.com/web/guest/whats-new\"><u data-renderer-mark=\"true\">What’s New with Liferay</u></a></p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"21673\">For detailed instructions on upgrading your Liferay DXP instance, please refer to our <a data-renderer-mark=\"true\" href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/w/dxp/installation-and-upgrades/upgrading-liferay\" title=\"https://learn.liferay.com/w/dxp/installation-and-upgrades/upgrading-liferay\"><u data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Upgrading Liferay</u></a> documentation.</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"21795\">Read Liferay’s <a data-renderer-mark=\"true\" href=\"https://www.liferay.com/liferay-service-life-policy\" title=\"https://www.liferay.com/liferay-service-life-policy\"><u data-renderer-mark=\"true\">service life policy</u></a> in order to understand how this change may affect you.</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"21888\">Please contact your Sales Contact or Customer Experience Manager to discuss upgrading to a supported version.</p>\n\t</li>\n</ul>"
      },
